                            <comment id="12664335" author="vsiveton" created="Fri, 16 Jan 2009 00:05:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch contains:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fixed some TODO about logging used and improved others&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;used filtering tag in the POMs to specify logging level for the tests. By default, the level is OFF but you could always call mvn test -Djava.util.logging.test.level=INFO or similar to see logs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fixed some header license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
